text: Findo Mdiza (born 7 March 1995) is a South African cricketer. He made his List A debut against Gauteng on 9 April 2016 in the final of the 2015–16 CSA Provincial One-Day Challenge. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1995 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:North West cricketers
